	<p n="1">
		Fortune!
	</p>
	
	<p n="1-2">
		Fourteenth <supplied reason="subaudible">year</supplied> of Tantippōttaraiyar<note>Sanskrit Dantin + Tamil Pōttaraiyar.</note>.
	</p>
	
	<p n="3-4">
		That which Ilāṭiḷavaraiyar had built.
	</p>	
	
	<p n="4-5">
		That which Ilāṭiḷavaraiciyār had built.
	</p>
	
	<p n="5-6">
		The feet of he who protects this are on my head.
